  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1203500/extras/52d1402166b46ab2b2c4f226b2f8bede.avif?t=1687975728\" width=500 height=262 /></span><br><strong>Dorky Fork</strong> is an indie game in which you need to arrange cubes to complete levels.<br><br><br>Take a journey through diverse and vibrant stages and then use <strong>ingame level editor</strong> to create your own puzzles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Challenging levels<br></li><li>Dreamy soundtrack by <strong>there will be nø sadness</strong><br></li><li>Colorful graphics<br></li><li>Ingame editor<br></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1203500/extras/52d1402166b46ab2b2c4f226b2f8bede.avif?t=1687975728\" width=500 height=262 /></span><br><strong>Dorky Fork</strong> is an indie game in which you need to arrange cubes to complete levels.<br><br><br>Take a journey through diverse and vibrant stages and then use <strong>ingame level editor</strong> to create your own puzzles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Challenging levels<br></li><li>Dreamy soundtrack by <strong>there will be nø sadness</strong><br></li><li>Colorful graphics<br></li><li>Ingame editor<br></li></ul>",
